   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"Aurelius Hatres, son of Chairas and Rhodia, of the village of Euhemeria, to Aurelia Apia, greetings. I shall give as dowry for your daughter Nonna a linen dress of the Dalmatian kind with a purple border, one face-cloth, a head-band, one Tarsian bath towel, and a pair of sandals, in the month of Pharmouthi."</ab>
         </div>
